generated by integrated business of these enterprises within the supply
chain. It is precisely because of this fact that, when an enterprise
creates a unique system of goods and information flow with other members
of the chain, it in fact enhances the efficiency of managing the entire
chain. In that way, the value of the whole system increases for the
